请大家提前办理选课手续以保证有充足的机位，（发信告知姓名、所在系、学号、班号、email,以便发送课程信息和资料。）
课程内容：
This course is typically organized into the four modules:
PART 1 Languages for geometrical dimensioning and tolerancing (8h)
PART 2 Functional tolerancing (8h)
PART 3 Manufacturing and statistical tolerancing (8h)
PART 4 Geometrical Metrology (8h)
